      <title>中国开发商万科被穆迪评为垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/chinese-developer-vanke-cut-to-junk-territory-by-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级取消了国有开发商万科企业的投资级信用评级，并警告可能进一步下调信用评级，并预测由于房屋销售下降和融资不确定性，信贷指标和流动性将减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/chinese-developer-vanke-cut-to-junk-territory-by-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 12:54:36 GMT</pubDate>
