      <title>Hinduja 律师称人口贩卖起诉书存在缺陷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/hinduja-lawyers-say-human-trafficking-indictment-flawed-needs-to-be-re-examined</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因虐待家政人员而被控贩卖人口的亿万富翁欣杜贾家族成员表示，瑞士针对他们的起诉书存在严重缺陷，必须发回检察官重新审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/hinduja-lawyers-say-human-trafficking-indictment-flawed-needs-to-be-re-examined</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 11:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
